2016.06.24
This is sourcecode of DCASE Challenge 2016 Task 1. http://www.cs.tut.fi/sgn/arg/dcase2016/task-acoustic-scene-classification
Using Mel + DNN achieve 74.8% accuracy on the 0-th fold

THIS CODE IS MIT LISCENCED. 
AUTHOR: QIUQIANG KONG, q.kong@surrey.ac.uk
CVSSP, UNIVERSITY OF SURREY

======================================

Pre-requiste python packages:
librosa
hat

Usage:
------ Preparation ------
* modify the paths of dataset in config.py

------ Development Cross Validation ------
* run prepare_dev_data.py 	Calculate features for development data
* run main_dev_dnn.py 		Train model on cross validation of development data
* run main_dev_recognize.py 	Generate results and evaluate on cross validation data

------ Testing of Private Data ------
1. run prepare_eva_data.py	Calculate features for evaluation data
2. run main_eva_dnn.py		Train model on all development data
3. run main_eva_recognize.py	Generate Results of private data. Result is in 'Results/task1_results.txt'
